oss with hero.\n\n**Dread Abominations will spawn if a player reaches 33 corruption\n\n**allocate any corruption to a sleeping player if possible\n\n!!@33 corruption the player with 33 corroption must avoid crushing shadows on the ground\n\n!!@66 corruption the player with 66 corruption must avoid pink swirlies on the ground\n\n!!@100 nightmare the player receives 300% dmg buff for 20secs and then becomes MCed",
